---
title: Quick Sesame Crumbed Katsu Chicken with Rapid Rice & Creamy Slaw
description: Katsu sauce is like the superhero sidekick of Japanese cuisine - bold, flavourful, and ready to take your tastebuds on an adventure! Pour it over a golden crumbed chicken dotted with sesame seeds, and watch as every bite become a delicious thrill ride.
